   "explain_en": "Means to stay in a place until someone comes or something happens.\n\n例：駅で友達を待つ。\nI wait for my friend at the station.",
   "explain_ja": "人や物事が来るまで同じ場所にいて、その時を過ごすことです。\n\n例：駅で友達を待つ。",
